---
description: Triggers the create-website skill when user asks to create a new website, store, or site
globs: src/websites/**/*
alwaysApply: false
---

When the user asks to create a new website, new store, or new site:

1. Read and follow `.cursor/skills/create-website/SKILL.md`
2. Also follow `.cursor/skills/atlagia-ecommerce-frontend/SKILL.md` for design and style rules
3. Never modify core files — all work goes in `src/websites/<StoreName>/`
4. `PUBLIC_SITE_NAME` in `.env` must match the folder name exactly (case-sensitive)
5. Every website needs its own `components/` folder with real `.astro` files
6. Use MCP browser verification after each visual milestone
